<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text">​</span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text">Paithal Clinic is a trusted paediatric healthcare center located in Cherthala, committed to ensuring the health, happiness, and well-being of children. Led by Dr. Neethu Mohan, the clinic focuses on delivering ethical, attentive, and child-friendly medical care in a warm and comfortable environment.</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text">We understand that children need more than treatment &mdash; they need reassurance, kindness, and careful attention at every step.</p></div><!--/$--></section><!--/$--><!--$--><section id="comp-mmexib2i" tabindex="-1" data-block-level-container="Section" class="xuzjBY comp-mmexib2i wixui-section Gzsk0j" data-testid="section-container"><div id="bgLayers_comp-mmexib2i" data-hook="bgLayers" data-motion-part="BG_LAYER comp-mmexib2i" class="MW5IWV"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="LWbAav Kv1aVt"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-mmexib2i" data-motion-part="BG_MEDIA comp-mmexib2i" class="VgO9Yg"></div></div><div data-testid="responsive-container-content" class="comp-mmexib2i-container max-width-container"><!--$--><div id="comp-mmexivm5" class="ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mmexivm5 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_2 wixui-rich-text__text">Our Services</h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mmexj7bl" data-testid="imageX" class="lyNaha comp-mmexj7bl JdNFxG wixui-image"><div class="h1DYhE" data-motion-part="BG_LAYER comp-mmexj7bl"><div data-motion-part="BG_MEDIA comp-mmexj7bl"><wow-image id="img-comp-mmexj7bl" data-is-responsive="true" data-image-info="{&quot;containerId&quot;:&quot;comp-mmexj7bl&quot;,&quot;alignType&quot;:&quot;center&quot;,&quot;parallaxSpeed&quot;:1.5,&quot;sourceSets&quot;:[{&quot;focalPoint&quot;:{&quot;x&quot;:50,&quot;y&quot;:50},&quot;crop&quot;:{&quot;x&quot;:0,&quot;y&quot;:196,&quot;width&quot;:554,&quot;height&quot;:351,&quot;svgId&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;flip&quot;:&quot;none&quot;},&quot;displayMode&quot;:&quot;fill&quot;,&quot;scrollEffect&quot;:&quot;none&quot;,&quot;mediaQuery&quot;:&quot;(min-width: 320px) and (max-width: 750px)&quot;},{&quot;focalPoint&quot;:{&quot;x&quot;:50,&quot;y&quot;:50},&quot;crop&quot;:{&quot;x&quot;:0,&quot;y&quot;:194,&quot;width&quot;:554,&quot;height&quot;:308,&quot;svgId&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;flip&quot;:&quot;none&quot;},&quot;displayMode&quot;:&quot;fill&quot;,&quot;scrollEffect&quot;:&quot;none&quot;,&quot;mediaQuery&quot;:&quot;(min-width: 320px) and (max-width: 1000px)&quot;}],&quot;imageData&quot;:{&quot;uri&quot;:&quot;3006e6_d3ed5a90196f4d17896f77a5c40ff85b~mv2.jpg&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:554,&quot;height&quot;:744,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;c64182ea124a4464c4ba42914aff3631.jpg&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;c64182ea124a4464c4ba42914aff3631.jpg&quot;,&quot;displayMode&quot;:&quot;fill&quot;,&quot;focalPoint&quot;:{&quot;x&quot;:50,&quot;y&quot;:38},&quot;scrollEffect&quot;:&quot;none&quot;},&quot;hasAnimation&quot;:false,&quot;encoding&quot;:&quot;AVIF&quot;,&quot;allowFullGIFTransformation&quot;:false}" data-has-ssr-src="true" data-motion-part="BG_IMG comp-mmexj7bl" class="Ux33nC"><picture><source media="(min-width: 320px) and (max-width: 750px)" srcSet="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/3006e6_d3ed5a90196f4d17896f77a5c40ff85b~mv2.jpg/v1/crop/x_0,y_196,w_554,h_351/fill/w_100,h_63,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_auto/c64182ea124a4464c4ba42914aff3631.jpg"/><source media="(min-width: 320px) and (max-width: 1000px)" srcSet="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/3006e6_d3ed5a90196f4d17896f77a5c40ff85b~mv2.jpg/v1/crop/x_0,y_194,w_554,h_308/fill/w_100,h_55,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_auto/c64182ea124a4464c4ba42914aff3631.jpg"/><img loading="lazy" src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/3006e6_d3ed5a90196f4d17896f77a5c40ff85b~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_100,h_134,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/c64182ea124a4464c4ba42914aff3631.jpg" alt="c64182ea124a4464c4ba42914aff3631.jpg" style="object-fit:cover;object-position:50% 38%"/></picture></wow-image></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mmexkcmi" class="ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mmexkcmi wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Consultation</span><br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
As a paediatric specialist, my consultation service is centered on providing a personalized and thoughtful approach to your child&rsquo;s healthcare. I am committed to offering individual attention during every visit, ensuring that each child receives a careful clinical evaluation tailored to their unique needs and stage of development.</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text">During the consultation, I take time to listen attentively to parents&rsquo; concerns, conduct a thorough examination, and provide clear, comprehensive explanations about your child&rsquo;s health. My goal is not only to diagnose and treat but also to guide and reassure families with honest, evidence-based medical advice.</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text">Together, we will address your questions, monitor your child&rsquo;s growth and well-being, and foster a deeper understanding of their health &mdash; empowering you to make informed decisions with confidence and peace of mind.</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text">​</span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Growth &amp; Development Monitoring</span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text">Regular assessment of physical, emotional, and developmental milestones. Early identification and guidance to ensure healthy growth at every stage.</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text">​</span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Immune Health Guidance</span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text">Personalized medical consultation provided directly by the doctor, focused on supporting your child&rsquo;s immune health. Evidence-based guidance is offered to help strengthen immunity, prevent common illnesses, and promote overall well-being at every stage of childhood.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
One-on-one consultation with the doctor to support and strengthen your child&rsquo;s immune health through evidence-based medical guidance.</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text">​</span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Fever &amp; Infection Managemen</span>t</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text">Accurate diagnosis and effective treatment for fevers and common infections. Prompt care to ensure quick recovery and comfort for your child.</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text">​</span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Newborn Care &amp; Infant Checkups</span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text">Specialized care for newborns and infants during their crucial early months. Monitoring feeding, growth, immunity, and developmental progress.</p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text">​</span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Parental Guidance &amp; Counseling</span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text">Dedicated time for parents to discuss concerns, receive expert medical advice, and gain confidence in managing their child&rsquo;s health and well-being.</p></div><!--/$--></div></section><!--/$--><!--$--><section id="comp-mmal97d7" tabindex="-1" data-block-level-container="Section" class="xuzjBY comp-mmal97d7 wixui-section Gzsk0j" data-testid="section-container"><div id="bgLayers_comp-mmal97d7" data-hook="bgLayers" data-motion-part="BG_LAYER comp-mmal97d7" class="MW5IWV"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="LWbAav Kv1aVt"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-mmal97d7" data-motion-part="BG_MEDIA comp-mmal97d7" class="VgO9Yg"></div></div><div data-testid="responsive-container-content" class="comp-mmal97d7-container max-width-container"><!--$--><div id="comp-mmal9eet" role="" class="PiVxGu MDrwHQ comp-mmal9eet wixui-box" dir="ltr"><div aria-hidden="true" class="yPXgy9 YqUfCX inner-box wixui-box"></div><div data-testid="responsive-container-content" class="comp-mmal9eet-container"><!--$--><div id="comp-mmagow033" class="ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mmagow033 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_2 wixui-rich-text__text">Our Services</h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mmahesc0" class="ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mmahesc0 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Consultation</span><br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
